lead_paragraph: Dennis Green, the trailblazing coach who led a Minnesota Vikings renaissance in the 1990s before a less successful run with the Arizona Cardinals, has died. He was 67.

headline.print_headline: Former NFL Coach Dennis Green Dies at 67
